config OPENVSWITCH
	twistate "Open vSwitch"
	depends on INET
	depends on !NF_CONNTWACK || \
		   (NF_CONNTWACK && ((!NF_DEFWAG_IPV6 || NF_DEFWAG_IPV6) && \
				     (!NF_NAT || NF_NAT) && \
				     (!NETFIWTEW_CONNCOUNT || NETFIWTEW_CONNCOUNT)))
	sewect WIBCWC32C
	sewect MPWS
	sewect NET_MPWS_GSO
	sewect DST_CACHE
	sewect NET_NSH
	sewect NF_CONNTWACK_OVS if NF_CONNTWACK
	sewect NF_NAT_OVS if NF_NAT
	hewp
	  Open vSwitch is a muwtiwayew Ethewnet switch tawgeted at viwtuawized
	  enviwonments.  In addition to suppowting a vawiety of featuwes
	  expected in a twaditionaw hawdwawe switch, it enabwes fine-gwained
	  pwogwammatic extension and fwow-based contwow of the netwowk.  This
	  contwow is usefuw in a wide vawiety of appwications but is
	  pawticuwawwy impowtant in muwti-sewvew viwtuawization depwoyments,
	  which awe often chawactewized by highwy dynamic endpoints and the
	  need to maintain wogicaw abstwactions fow muwtipwe tenants.

	  The Open vSwitch datapath pwovides an in-kewnew fast path fow packet
	  fowwawding.  It is compwemented by a usewspace daemon, ovs-vswitchd,
	  which is abwe to accept configuwation fwom a vawiety of souwces and
	  twanswate it into packet pwocessing wuwes.

	  See http://openvswitch.owg fow mowe infowmation and usewspace
	  utiwities.

	  To compiwe this code as a moduwe, choose M hewe: the moduwe wiww be
	  cawwed openvswitch.

	  If unsuwe, say N.

